               <msContents>
                  <summary>Vision of Sinoda, ራዕየ፡ ሲኖደ፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="22v"/><title>Vision of Sinoda, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ራዕየ፡ ሲኖደ፡</foreign></title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                  <note>Excerpt from the Vision of Sinoda, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ራዕየ፡ ሲኖደ፡</foreign>, regarding the mystical king, Tewodros</note>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1"><locus from="1r" to="1v"/><title>Introduction</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ቅዱስ፡ ሥሉስ፡ አምላክነ፡ ዋህድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ሥሉስ፡ በተዋህዶቱ፡ ለእመ፡ ኃሠሥኮ፡ ትረክቦ፡ በኀበ፡ ወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ከመ ዝ፡ ምሥጢረ፡ እምነትነ፡ በመለኮቱ፡ ለአልፋ። ነገር፡ ዘከመ፡ ርእየ፡ አባ፡ ሲኖዳ፡ ራእየ፡ ርእየ፤ እምኀበ፡ አምላክ፡ ፲ተ፡ ራእያተ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2"><locus from="2r" to="22v"/><title>Vision of Sinoda</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ንዌጥን በእንተ፡ አይ፡ ዘርእየ፡ አባ፡ ሲኦኣ፡ ፲ተ፡ ራእያተ፡ ፯ ራእያት፡ በእንተ፡ ነገሥት፡ እለ፡ ይመልክዎን፡ ለ፯ብሔር፡ ፰ራእይ፡ ተስፋ፡ ጻድቃን፡ ወፍግዓ፡ ተድላሆሙ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                </msItem>
              </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="23r" to="33r"/><title>Book of mystery, <foreign xml:lang="gez">መጽሐፈ፡ ምሥጢር፡</foreign></title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ካዕበኒ፡ ይቤ፡ አባ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ዘኢትዮጵያ። በእንተ፡ ምጽአቱ፡ ለውእቱ፡ ንጉሥ፡ በውስተ፡ መጽሐፉ፡ ዘይሰመይ። መጽሐፈ፡ ምሥጢር፡ ወበእንተ፡ ርደተ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ገሀደ፡ እንዘ፡ ይሬእይዎ፡ ኵሉ፡ ዓለም።</incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                  <note>Excerpt from the Book of mystery, <foreign xml:lang="gez">መጽሐፈ፡ ምሥጢር፡</foreign>, on the Prophecy of Abba Giyorgis of Ethiopia regarding the mystical king of Ethiopia [Tewodros]</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="33r" to="34v"/><title>The Prophecy of Saint Victor regarding the mystical king of Ethiopia [Tewodros]</title><incipit xml:lang="gez"><gap reason="omitted"/> ይቤ ፊቅጦር፡ ወልደ፡ ማርታ፡ ወእምይእቲ፡ እለት፡ ይከውን፡ ፍስሐ፡ ወሰላም፡ ውስተ፡ ኵሉ፡ ዓለም። <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
